 time filmmakers their break teen sips with stephen berra harlem aria with bill jennings matt dillions directorial debut city of ghosts jonathan newmans swinging with the finkels and foster mahesh mathais bhopal express and broken thread eli craigs directorial debut tucker and dale vs evil which won the audience award at sxsw festival and pat holdenss when the lights went out nayar is currently working alongside reliance entertainment as an executive producer the first film he collaborated on was with julia roberts on jesus henry christ which was followed by safe starring jason statham subsequent films under the partnership are dredd d starring karl urban a haunted house starring marlon wayans bullet to the head starring sylvester stallone dead man down starting colin farrell noomi rapace hummingbird starring jason statham and enchanted kingdom a documentary about africa as a producer he produced films walking with dinosaurs d paranoia starring gary oldman and harrison ford and vampire academy starring zoey deutch and lucy fry he has also had a notable career in tv production producing episodic series on the air for abc hotel malibu  second chances for cbs white dwarf with fox and hotel room for hbo his most recent tv series includes executive producing sense  for netflix directed by andy and lana wachowski in  nayar successfully opened the highly rated bend it like beckham  the musical based on the hit movie in londons west end phoenix theatre quickly becoming a critics favourite nayar is partner in india take one productions a production services company based in los angeles and india some of the notable films they have worked are holy smoke alexander the great slumdog millionaire eat pray love mission impossible  ghost protocol looking for comedy in muslim world life of pi zero dark thirty million dollar arm and the best exotic marigold hotel    nayar is also a partner in atlantic screen music a music publishing company i m global a foreign sales organization georgeville tv a tv production company in addition nayar is also serving as an executive producer on open road films that he is financing under a multipicture multiyear deal thru his company riverstone pictures which he launched in london in oct  through the same company he also financed and is an executive producer on genius starring colin firth nicole kidman jude law which is in production currently he is producing viceroy house which is being directed by gurinder chadha and his next feature is second objective written by mark frost which will shoot later this year other upcoming feature films are graceling paladin prophecy and citizens of london all based on bestsellers donated by deepak nayaradditional lot details valid for  person a meal is part of the event the meal cost is included the winner may take a photo the winner can take something small to be signed cannot be resold or reauctioned cannot be transferred expires  year from the close of auction travel and accommodations are not included we expect all winning bidders and their guests to conduct themselves appropriately when attending an experience won at charitybuzz polite manners and respect for the generous donor and adherence to any rules or parameters are a must to be scheduled at a mutually agreed upon date based on the donors availability lot shipping detailsthe minimum processing and handling charge for this item is  the minimum shipping handling and applicable insurance charge for nontangible items is  detailed redemption information will be emailed to the winning bidder the minimum shipping charge for hard copies of tickets and certificates is  the minimum shipping charge for merchandise is  shipments outside the us are subject to additional shipping and customs fees tickets certificates and merchandise are typically shipped with signature required unless otherwise specified via professional carrier in some cases tickets will be left at the venues will call window under the winners name merchandise 